name: It's a Trap! - D&D 3.5E theme
description: # It's A Trap! - D&D 3.5 theme_v3.0 updates:_* Updated the trap theme to be compatible with Its A Trap v3.0.This is a D&D 3.5 trap theme built to support Diana P.'s 3.5 Edition character sheet.To use this theme for the It's A Trap! script, enter 'DnD-3.5' for the ```theme``` user option.
